"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Skeleton","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSThemesOrange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider/skeletonColorGradientMiddle":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider\/skeletonColorGradientMiddle","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeskeletoncomponenttokensprovider\/skeletoncolorgradientmiddle","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"skeletonColorGradientMiddle"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticTokens","text":"MultipleColorSemanticTokens"}],"role":"symbol","title":"skeletonColorGradientMiddle","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value  colors.colorOpacityLower"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol"}}}